item.title: Need Vocals? Check out these people!
item.dc:creator: brandnaqua
item.description:
My vocals are admittedly poor, but thank-you for putting me on this list. To be more specific I am better at writing songs or ghostwriting raps then recording them over tracks as preferably demos. Then with the lyrics and demo track you guys could go ahead and find a vocalist who can execute your vision better! I could try my best to do vocals if anyone really wants, but since I don’t have the best equipment yet or top level skill it’s a bit more challenging to get the optimal results right now. But for written songs, hit me up with a mood, intention, storyline, point of view, topic or subjects and I can write for you guys! So much talent in the Auxy community and i’d love to collab with you guys in that way.
